name: RHD 14
description:
Zarafshan Range in Tajikistan made from 1-arcsecond Shuttle Radar Topography Mission (SRTM) digital elevation model. DEM data is processed using Topographic Openness and Slope algorithms and blending in QGIS. Different color ramps are tested before selecting the final one that “feels right” for the overall mood of the image as some color ramps are more cheerful and bright, while others are more subdued. 3630 x 3630 px.

Mesmerizing layers of relief, height and depth.
